To flash bootloader:

  make bhbl.bin
  ./flash-bl.sh

To build main code:

  make main.bin

To upload code to HAT running bootloader:

  make upload
  ./upload /dev/ttyUSB0 main.bin   # change serial device as required

Interactive session with bootloader or main code:

  picocom -b3000000 /dev/ttyUSB0   # change serial device as required

